sub_title: Order Management Coordinator at Canon EMEA
summary: I am a university graduate and have a degree in international academic studies for German and Chinese. I also have fluent knowledge of Russian and Dutch alongside my knowledge of the English language. I specialize in translation work, but I have had experience writing texts for tours and doing research for tours as well. Additionaly I have experience working in logistics and customer service in an international environment and in order management for the DACH, Benelux and Nordic regions.
